trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of conceptual model to code namespace mappings.
The namespace mappings are used by the <xref:System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator> class to specify a different code namespace for generating code than what is specified in the CSDL file.
The namespace mappings are consulted when a reference to a type is to be generated.
If an entry is found, the value will be used to generate the qualified reference to the type; otherwise, the CSDL namespace will be used.
Adds a namespace mapping to the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EdmToObjectNamespaceMap"></xref>.
The model namespace name.
The code namespace name.
Removes all namespace mappings from the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EdmToObjectNamespaceMap"></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EdmToObjectNamespaceMap"></xref> contains the specified model namespace name.
The model namespace name.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the model namespace name is found; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets the number of mappings in the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EdmToObjectNamespaceMap"></xref>.
The number of mappings.
Gets the list of model namespace names in the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EdmToObjectNamespaceMap"></xref>.
The list of model namespace names.
Gets or sets the code namespace name of the specified model namespace name.
The model namespace name.
The code namespace name that maps to the specified model namespace name.
Removes the specified namespace mapping.
The model namespace mapping to remove.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the namespace mapping was successfully removed; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether the object namespace was retrieved.
The model namespace name.
The code namespace name.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the object namespace was retrieved; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
